Market Analysis and Size

Nowadays, vehicles are equipped with numerous innovative technologies that differ in performance, costs, functions and applications. Vehicle becomes more comfortable for the traveler with the use of these features. Battery management is essential for acquiring maximum performance during variety of situations.

The battery thermal management system assists in regulating the battery's thermal behavior. Global Battery Thermal System Market was valued at USD 1478.58 million in 2021 and is expected to reach USD 1947.01 million by 2029, registering a CAGR of 3.50% during the forecast period of 2022-2029. Battery Electric Vehicle (BEV) accounts for the largest vehicle type segment in the respective market owing to the availability of subsidies and support from the government. The market report curated by the Data Bridge Market Research team includes in-depth expert analysis, import/export analysis, pricing analysis, production consumption analysis, and pestle analysis.

